<p>
<lb n="1"/>tirumakaḷ po
<lb n="2" break="no"/>lap perunilaccelvi
<lb n="3" break="no"/>yun taṉakke Urimai pūṇṭamai ma
<lb n="4" break="no"/>ṉakkoḷa kāntaḷur cālai kalamaṟut
<lb n="5" break="no"/>taruḷi veṅkaināṭuṅ kaṅkapāṭiyu nu
<lb n="6" break="no"/>ḷampapāṭiyun taṭikaipāṭiyuṅ kuṭa
<lb n="7" break="no"/>malaināṭuṅ kollamuṅ kaliṅ
<lb n="8" break="no"/>kamu meṇṭicai nikaḻtara Īḻa maṇṭa
<lb n="9" break="no"/>lamun tiṇṭiṟal veṉṟit taṇṭā
<lb n="10" break="no"/>l koṇṭu taṉṉeḻilvaḷa ruḻiyuḷe
<lb n="11" break="no"/>llā yāṇṭut toḻutaka <unclear>viḷaṅkum yā</unclear>
<lb n="12" break="no"/>ṇṭey ceḻiyarait <unclear>te</unclear>cukoḷ ko
<lb n="13" break="no"/>rācake<hi rend="grantha"><unclear>śa</unclear></hi>rivaṟmarākiya I<unclear>rā</unclear><hi rend="grantha">ja</hi>rā<hi rend="grantha">jade</hi>
<lb n="14" break="no"/>varkku yāṇ<unclear>ṭu</unclear> <num value="19"><g type="numeral">10</g> 9</num> Āvatu <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="15"/>tevavaḷanāṭṭu Iṭaiyaḷanāṭṭu perun<note n="204-1">Lines 16 to 19 badly damaged.</note>
</p>

